  "description": [
    "i So Labor May Know Its time for hysterical witch hunt ing and name calling to stop Both are dirty unsportsmanlike pastimes Both are practiced by un reasonable men and women who sub stitute loud noise for sound judgment Those who express liberal view points are too often damn Com mies Those who express conserva tive viewpoints are too often called dirty Fascists And those who sit on the sidelines and listen become more confused and nauseated as the farce goes on The recent investigation of the movie industry was a disgraceand the House UnAmerican Activities Committee should be soundly con demned for its actions The condemnation should be aimed at the tactics used by the Committee not at the fact that a committee named by Congress decided to investi gate an industry No groupjudicial or legislative should be permitted to serve as prose cutor judge jury and executioner The UnAmerican Activities Com mittee assumed all of these roles No person should be required to testify about his own beliefs or acts unless given an ample opportunity to confront and crossquestion those mak ing accusations Some of the nations newspapers re cently told an interesting and dis gusting story about"
  ],
